params.description: The parent resource. This may be "projects/{project}", "folders/{folder}", or "organizations/{organization}".

params.name: data.filter
params.description: A filter on the type of approval requests to retrieve. Must be one of the following values: [not set]: Requests that are pending or have active approvals. ALL: All requests. PENDING: Only pending requests. ACTIVE: Only active (i.e. currently approved) requests. DISMISSED: Only requests that have been dismissed, or requests that are not approved and past expiration. EXPIRED: Only requests that have been approved, and the approval has expired. * HISTORY: Active, dismissed and expired requests.
